<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
<strong>@HI{{tatte}}</strong> is used to mean that even if something were done or something were in some state,
the desired result would not come about.

<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{ano@KJ{{person}}niha@KJ{{tale}}shi<strong>tatte</strong>@KJ{{part}}karimasenn.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      Even if I tell him he won't understand.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</p>

<h2> Notes </h2>

<p>
<strong>@HI{{tatte}}</strong> is used only in informal Japanese.
</p>

